&gt;  The
&gt; &gt; entrance of the base was more or less repaired; they replaced the doors
&gt; and
&gt; &gt; found replacement parts for the defense systems and shields.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; Setting the last of his belongings on a shelf in the commander&#39;s office,
&gt; he
&gt; &gt; wondered what had become of the previous maximal commander.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; Accessing the radio panel on his desk, he tuned to maximal bands and
&gt; picked
&gt; &gt; up the microphone.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &quot;This is Lord Perseus to all maximals and allies.    What is your
&gt; status?&quot;
